title: FOSS4G Auckland 2025
content: Join open source geospatial users, developers, and researchers from around the world for the global FOSS4G conference, taking place November 17-23 in Auckland, New Zealand. The 2025 program is packed with QGIS-focused presentations and workshops, making it an invaluable event for all QGIS users in the region. Double-click this entry to check out the conference program and to purchase tickets.
